[30;1m139 | [0m[35m        checked against a domain name that includes the dot. In addition, some[0m

[30;1m141 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m142 | [0m[35m        However, the hostname with trailing dot is critical to DNS resolution; doing a[0m
[30;1m143 | [0m[35m        lookup with the trailing dot will properly only resolve the appropriate FQDN,[0m
